#### Eldritch Chain
*Prerequisite: 5th level* <br/>
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

When you hit a target with your eldritch blast, you can cause it to jump to a secondary target within 30 feet. Make another attack roll; on a hit, the target takes one less die of damage. For example, if you deal 3d8 damage to your first target, the next target takes 2d8 damage. 

You may repeat this process until you run out of eldritch damage dice or you miss. Each new target must be within 30 feet of the previous target and you can't target the same creature more than once.

You cannot combine this invocation with those that allow your eldritch blast to affect an area or hit multiple targets. 

